  {
    "key": "0953f1eb0dafc485242d99823b4bf4edae5750917b48f7a935a75acc228dc570",
    "original": "This draft, synthesized from the faint ectoplasmic remnants of a 'slain' Geist, alters the body of whoever imbibes it to take on a similar ghostly aspect. Any weapons wielded by such a warrior will surely gain some of the creature's ability to bypass armor! Auditory hallucinations are an expected side effect of consuming the draft and will likely cease after a while. Hopefully, anyway.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "this.m.Description = \"This draft, synthesized from the faint ectoplasmic remnants of a 'slain' Geist, alters the body of whoever imbibes it to take on a similar ghostly aspect. Any weapons wielded by such a warrior will surely gain some of the creature's ability to bypass armor! Auditory hallucinations are an expected side effect of consuming the draft and will likely cease after a while. Hopefully, anyway.\""
  },
